name: Team Tower Defense - Competitive MMO Style Tower Defense!
blurb: Multiplayer based Tower Defense with a unique feel. Multiple builders, A lot of customization. Highly competitive, A lot of fun!

rewards.reward: [Contributor] Receive a virtual high five for being awesome!
[Recognition] Receive a special thanks on the website which will stay there forever.

[That's My Name!] + [All Prior Rewards] Reserve your username! Tired of waiting to play a game, only to have your favorite username taken? We feel ya. You can reserve your username so it will be available to you at all times! (Unfortunately, it's a first come first serve in regards to others trying to register the same name).

[Founder] + [All Prior Rewards] This will open access to a special Founder builder and a Founder Badge on the forums and in-game. Also, receive guaranteed access to our beta tests! (including closed betas) You will also receive access to the beta forums where you can give your feedback to a section where developers will actively monitor!

[Snail Mail Thank You] + [All Prior Rewards] Receive a post card from the developers saying "Thank You!" it will include a customized design with all of our signatures. I mean, lets be honest. Who wouldn't want our signature? You will also receive $5 worth of Merc Credits.

[I'm The Alpha!] + [All Prior Rewards] Guaranteed Early Alpha Access* as well as a kick ass Cape for your builders! Yeah...A cape! Although the capes are clearly for aesthetic purposes, who wouldn't want to make their builder resemble Super Man?

Also, receive $10 worth of Merc Credits.

***Alpha access might be open to limited slots at certain times, so we can't allow thousands of people to just openly flood the server. We will however attempt to work something out so everyone has a chance to play***
[Sub It Up] + [All Prior Rewards] Receive a 6 month subscription once the game is released. Also, you will get $15 worth of Merc Credits.

[At Least A Rookie] + [All Prior Rewards] How's a 1 year Subscription sound? Pretty good huh? Okay. We'll also give you... 5 Beta invites and 2 alpha invites! So you and 7 of your buddies can play together! And you get $20 worth of Merc Credits.

[Official Swag Bag] + [All Prior Rewards] The "Swag Bag" which includes a Team TD T-Shirt, a kick ass high quality poster for your bedroom (The chicks will dig it), and other little goodies we may or may not include in the form of wearable items..\r\nAnd deck out yourself in game with $25 worth of Merc Credits.

[Date My Avatar] + [All Prior Rewards] Receive your very own Custom Avatar! Avatars will be predesigned within the game allowing players to pick one. You can have your own custom one that NOBODY else can have! You will also receive 10 Beta invites to play with your friends.\r\nAnd receive $30 worth of Merc Credits.
[Really Sub It Up] + [All Prior Rewards] Receive a 3 Year Subscription, 10 Beta Invites, and 5 Alpha Invites!\r\nYou also receive $35 worth of Merc Credits.

[Producer] + [All Prior Rewards] In our game we have an oil rig which plays a rather large role in the success of your team. For $1,000 you can have your name on the Oil Rig in the form of a company! Example: "Cynikals Oil Co" or "Suck It Up, Oil Co". These will be modeled into the model itself and will remain as long as the game utilizes the oil rig facilities (So..Pretty much forever). If during the development phase, we change the oil rig into something else, you will be contacted and told of the change and you will be given the opportunity to give us a new name!

You will also receive a Producer Title and Badge!

Plus, you get $50 worth of Merc Credits.

[Build Me A Statue] + [All Prior Rewards] In the map, we will be placing statues. You can have a statue modeled after your favorite builder and have your name on the plaque. Note: The statue placement will either be random, or static based on the map / level design.

You will also get to select the pose of the builder for your statue!

In addition, you will get worth $75 of Merc Credits.

[Part Of The Game] + [All Prior Rewards] Now, this is the grand daddy of them all. You will sit down with us and we will hash out details and make a builder for you! Well, not JUST for you, but for everyone..But at least you would of helped design it! You will help name the units, determine what their special abilities do, what they look like, etc!

And you'll receive $100 worth of Merc Credits.

*Note: This is limited, and is NOT guaranteed within any amount of time. However, it will be implemented to the game at/before launch.
